              "text": "The Cabinet shall exercise in particularly the following functions:"
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "lists": [
        [
          {
            "text": "Helps in setting up the general policy of the State in collaboration with the President of the Republic and controlling its implementation in accordance with the laws and republican decrees."
          },
          {
            "text": "Directing, co-ordinating and following up the work of the ministries and their different administrations as well as public organizations and institutions."
          },
          {
            "text": "Issuing administrative and executive decisions in accordance with the laws and decrees and supervising their implementation."
          },
          {
            "text": "Preparing draft laws and decrees."
          },
          {
            "text": "Preparing the draft of the general budget of the State."
          },
          {
            "text": "Preparing the draft of the State's overall plan."
          },
          {
            "text": "Contracting and granting loans in accordance with the rules of the Constitution."
          },
          {
            "text": "Supervising the implementation of law, maintaining State security and protecting the rights of the citizens and the interests of the State."
          }
        ]
